{"type": "article", "id": 22519, "title": "甜甜圈式的包装", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-19T07:10:17Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 68, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702164701w9BpTMe8NHQyhv0f.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是墨西哥的平面设计工作室Super Magic Friend 为墨西哥一家新开的面包店设计的整体形象和包装，logo 就是一个被咬了一口的甜甜圈。紫色的甜甜圈上分布着彩色的小糖针，它们又分散到了整体的包装上，带给人一种梦幻的感觉，似乎已经尝到了甜甜圈带给人的美好。如果仔细看，logo 也像是一个带宇航员的水晶球或是一只眼睛，很有趣。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164658f2IgAc0V6WZU3yvN.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6712963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164659FVc0OqiXut4aR1D9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67592593\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164659Vjcug4HKlZBFdUPY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66481481\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164700lLhXYEMHtWrTIGfv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67685185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021647009ldM3UAufVZLK0mp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164701sjQ52qDVgelAJuBm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67407407\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n"}